questions.bestView: Sitting on the steps by the Sacre Coeur, looking back over Paris.
questions.interestingThing: Paris only has one stop sign in the entire city.
questions.favouriteMoment: Seeing the bridge where Inception was filmed.
questions.enjoyableMeal: Typically French, but a Beef bourguignon with a carafe of red wine in a small cafe in Montmartre.
questions.biggestSurprise: How you're able to visit Paris numerous times but are still able to find something new every time.
questions.topTip: Stay in a central location - it makes for a good base to go exploring from.
